: : Rodimus Prime : :

Finally Rodimus made his way outside the base. He transformes to his sports car mode and heads for the cannon at top speeds.


CatMaster o <CatMastero@...> wrote:
'This sounds bad' Kenzo thought.  He was a bit worried about what
Unicron might unleash.  He exited the Maximal base and took a glance
towards the sky before transforming to his helochopter form and taking
flight to the cannon construction site.
